            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8C%89%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E5%90%83%E9%A5%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8C%89%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E5%90%83%E9%A5%AD%E6%9C%89%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%8E%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#按这个顺序吃饭有利于控制体重#</span></a>】数据显示，我国6岁-17岁儿童青少年超重肥胖率近20%。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E8%83%96%E7%82%B9%E5%84%BF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E8%83%96%E7%82%B9%E5%84%BF%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%A1%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小时候胖点儿真的没关系吗#</span></a>？专家介绍，超重的儿童青少年，发生高血压、胆固醇异常等的风险更大，相关的健康危险还会持续到成年。对儿童青少年而言，控制体重的同时需注意营养均衡，循序渐进；可按“蔬菜—肉菜—主食”顺序进食，细嚼慢咽，每餐用时不少于20分钟。儿童青少年减肥跟成人还有哪些不同？👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4900190197579877" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hduc74lj9dj61uj11fb2902.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/O56nEzfvlx085lSmpUs001041201xSbE0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1683839699&amp;ssig=uQb6gTezFw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/koD7X5AXlx085lSkUV4Q01041200PCKI0E010.mp4?label=mp4_